title: I am not in ‘Aashiqui 3’; not paired opposite Hrithik Roshan in any film yet: Deepika Padukone
text: Hrithik Roshan Thursday, 22 October 2015 (13 minutes ago) Denying her presence in the movie 'Aashiqui 3' opposite Hrithik Roshan, Deepika Padukone told The IndianExpress.com, "I am not in Aashiqui 3."
